node.text:
skinny dipping is out in the world now! wrote this song and made this video with people that are the human embodiment of a hug!!

i am so grateful for you @juliamichaels @jpsaxe @leroyclampitt i love shoving little motion pictures in a first verse and love when a song can happen so effortlessly in between bathroom breaks and the moments where we can’t stop laughing. i love you sm!!! 
 
thank u amazing team for being crazy patient and ambitious and helping me bring something to life through such a personal lens so beautifully 
@amberpark @sarahcarpenter @volaramgmt @daniellepriano @jasonbolden @johnmumblo @andgavazzi @jillpowellglam @islandrecords @callaird @dantegiani  @fieldtrip_ 

and thank you to all of you who are listening :’)
